  <brief_title>Gemcitabine/Oxaliplatin (GEMOX) With or Without Erlotinib (Tarceva) in Advanced Biliary Tract Carcinoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase III Study of Gemcitabine/Oxaliplatin (GEMOX) With or Without Erlotinib in Unresectable, Metastatic Biliary Tract Carcinoma</official_title>
  <sponsors>
