  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether Gemcitabine/Oxaliplatin (GEMOX) with or
      without Erlotinib (Tarceva) is effective in the treatment of unresectable, metastatic biliary
      tract carcinoma.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is a phase III study of Gemcitabine/Oxaliplatin (GEMOX) with or without Erlotinib in
      unresectable, metastatic biliary tract carcinoma.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
